li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#makefile%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-number">2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> makefile函数</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#makefile%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95"><span class="toc-number">2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> makefile函数的基本语法</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#makefile%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-number">2.2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> makefile常用函数</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#makefile%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> makefile文本处理函数</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0subst"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 字符串替换函数subst</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0patsubst"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 模式字符串替换函数patsubst</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8E%BB%E7%A9%BA%E6%A0%BC%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0strip"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.3.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 去空格函数strip</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0findstring"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.4.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 查找字符串函数findstring</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0filter"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.5.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 过滤函数filter</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8F%8D%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0filter-out"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.6.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 反过滤函数filter-out</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0sort"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.7.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 排序函数sort</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8F%96%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0word"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.8.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 取单词函数word</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8F%96%E5%AD%97%E4%B8%B2%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0wordlist"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.9.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 取字串函数wordlist。</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E6%95%B0%E7%9B%AE%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0words"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.10.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 统计单词数目函数words</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8F%96%E9%A6%96%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0firstword"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.11.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 取首单词函数firstword</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%94%A8vpath%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90cflags%E7%9A%84%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84"><span class="toc-number">2.2.1.12.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 一个简单的应用：用VPATH中的值生成CFLAGS的查找路径</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#makefile%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8D%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-number">2.2.2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> makefile文件名操作函数</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8F%96%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0dir"><span class="toc-number">2.2.2.1.</span> 